Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
Vehicle.Vehicle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Vehicle extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a vehicle in the simulator.

Each vehicle has an identifier, a type (car, truck, motorcycle), a path (sequence of nodes), and entry/exit timestamps within the system.
